  "title": "Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Working Location: Kaki Bukit</strong></p><p><strong>Working Hours: 830am - 530pm</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $2500 - $3300</strong></p><p>We are looking for a <strong>responsible and detail-oriented Admin Assistant</strong> to support our daily office operations.</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>General administrative duties (filing, data entry, document preparation)</p></li><li><p>Handling emails, phone calls, and basic correspondence</p></li><li><p>Assist with invoices, purchase orders, and simple reporting</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with internal teams and external parties</p></li><li><p>Other ad-hoc administrative tasks as assigned</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>At least <strong>1–2 years of administrative experience</strong> preferred</p></li><li><p>Proficient in <strong>Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, Outlook)</strong></p></li><li><p>Able to work independently and meet deadlines</p></li><li><p>Good communication and organisational skills</p></li></ul><p><strong>Added Advantage:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Basic shipping / logistics experience</strong> (e.g. documentation, coordination with forwarders, delivery tracking) will be an advantage, but <strong>not mandatory</strong></p></li></ul>",
